headline: Online Advantages Publishes 2025 Guide to Ranking in Google's AI Overviews and Generative Search Results
summary: With Google's AI Overviews now appearing for roughly 13% of all search queries, according to a leading industry study published in March 2025, visibility in AI summaries is quickly becoming the new SEO battleground. Today, Online Advantages, a U.S.-based SEO and AI marketing agency in Mooresville, NC, released its definitive guide: How to Get Featured in Google's AI Overviews: A Guide to the New SEO. The content will be updated constantly.
